<section class="border-y border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-indigo-700">Choose your starting point</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 break-keep text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-slate-950 sm:text-4xl">무엇부터 읽어야 할까요?</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-blue-200 bg-white p-6">
        <span class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-blue-50 font-black text-blue-700">1</span>
        <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-slate-500">서비스를 직접 만들고 싶다</p>
        <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-black text-slate-950">Chatdox</h3>
        <%= link_to "구축 과정 살펴보기 →", chatdox_path, class: "mt-6 inline-block rounded text-sm font-bold text-blue-700 hover:text-blue-900 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-blue-500" %>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-violet-200 bg-white p-6">
        <span class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-violet-50 font-black text-violet-700">2</span>
        <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-slate-500">AI와 일하는 방식을 설계하고 싶다</p>
        <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-black text-slate-950">Claudox</h3>
        <%= link_to "협업 기록 살펴보기 →", claudox_path, class: "mt-6 inline-block rounded text-sm font-bold text-violet-700 hover:text-violet-900 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-violet-500" %>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-300 bg-slate-900 p-6 text-white">
        <span class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-slate-800 font-black text-slate-300">3</span>
        <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-slate-400">만드는 법과 일하는 법이 모두 필요하다</p>
        <h3 class="mt-2 break-keep text-xl font-black">두 기록을 함께 탐색</h3>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400">묶음 상품과 구매 조건은 아직 확정되지 않았습니다.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
